<div class="text-center mb-4">
    <div class="home-header d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
        <%= image_tag "cheese_icon.png", alt: "Cheese icon", class: "home-header-icon" %>
        <h1 class="mb-0">Winnipeg Cheesemongers</h1>
        <%= image_tag "cheese_icon.png", alt: "Cheese icon", class: "home-header-icon" %>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row justify-content-center mb-5">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead text-center">
            Welcome to Winnipeg Cheesemongers, a local shop proudly serving Winnipeg
            for the past five years with a carefully chosen selection of artisan cheeses
            from near and far. From locally crafted favourites to exceptional international
            varieties, we are passionate about helping our community discover quality cheese,
            new flavours, and old favourites in a welcoming and personal way.

            Use the links below to start exploring our collection, browse cheeses by category,
            or create an account to make your shopping experience even easier. Whether you are
            looking for something familiar or hoping to discover a new favourite,
            we invite you to take a look around and enjoy what Winnipeg Cheesemongers has to offer.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-4">
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                <h2 class="h4 card-title">Products</h2>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Browse the full cheese selection and view product details, prices, and availability.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-auto">
                    <%= link_to "Go to Products", products_path, class: "links" %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                <h2 class="h4 card-title">Categories</h2>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Explore cheeses by category so visitors can quickly find the type they want.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-auto">
                    <%= link_to "Go to Categories", categories_path, class: "links" %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                <h2 class="h4 card-title">Login</h2>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Sign in to your account to manage your profile, review your cart, and place orders.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-auto">
                    <%= link_to "Go to Login", new_customer_session_path, class: "links" %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
